    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the blood-soaked boots of Shevchenko, a battle-hardened nurse caught in the chaos of a zombie apocalypse.</strong><br>As the world crumbles, Shevchenko clings to one fragile hope — finding a cure. To do so, she must brave ruined cities, explore mysterious dungeons, and face off against grotesque undead nightmares. Survival is no guarantee. Curiosity is your only compass.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But this isn’t just your average dungeon crawler. Between ambushes and scavenging, you’ll also be answering delightfully absurd quizzes that <strong>reveal hidden sides of your personality</strong>—even the ones you didn’t know existed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306960/extras/d969aa75970d745ae0b479259272de4f.avif?t=1754034406\" width=386 height=480 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based dungeon-crawling RPG with a post-apocalyptic twist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bizarre personality quizzes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot, gear up, and face a terrifying variety of zombies and monsters</p></li></ul>",
